## <a id='cross'></a>Cross-platform Highlights

### <a id='new-errand'></a>BOSH Backup and Restore (BBR) 

BBR is a command-line tool for backing up and restoring BOSH deployments. You can use it to back up and restore PCF components. BBR is a beta feature in PCF v1.11. 

For more information, see the [Backing Up Pivotal Cloud Foundry with BBR](../customizing/backup-restore/backup-pcf-bbr.html) and [Restoring Pivotal Cloud Foundry from Backup with BBR](../customizing/backup-restore/backup-pcf-bbr.html) topics.

## <a id='services'></a>Services Highlights

- **PCF Metrics v1.4**: Simplifies tile installation, allows for custom metrics emitted from your app, provides instance level metrics visualization, and contains a significant update to the UI. 
For more information, see [PCF Metrics Release Notes and Known Issues](https://docs.pivotal.io/pcf-metrics/1-4/rn-ki.html).
- **JMX Bridge v1.9**: Contains overall security improvements, support for the Firehose tagged metric format, and the addition of a new optional feature that allows you to turn off the `opentsdb.nozzle` prepend which was present in previous versions. For more information, see [JMX Bridge Release Notes and Known Issues](https://docs.pivotal.io/jmx-bridge/1-9/rn-ki.html).


